      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:05:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出敲响警钟，特朗普交易充满矛盾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-exit-sounds-alarm-on-trump-trades-riven-with-contradiction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街在预测和交易关键选举方面有着糟糕的记录，即使是在最好的情况下也是如此。现在，随着乔·拜登的退出颠覆了美国总统竞选，根据最新的政治头条进行投资的危险性已凸显出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/biden-exit-sounds-alarm-on-trump-trades-riven-with-contradiction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 14:47:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
