      <title>匈牙利、斯洛伐克请求欧盟帮助乌克兰打击卢克石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/slovakia-warns-ukraine-on-fuel-after-kyiv-bars-lukoil-transit</link>
